dil &lt;unk&gt; hai ( english : the heart of the heart ) is a 2000 indian romantic drama film written and directed by aamir khan . the film stars salman khan , hrithik roshan , zeenat aman , and irrfan khan in lead roles . the film was a critical and commercial success , grossing over $ 100 million worldwide . it was the highest grossing bollywood film of all time .